programme.title: Live UEFA Nations League
programme.desc: Spain v England (Kick-off 7.45pm). Coverage of the League A Group Four clash at Estadio Benito Villamarin in Seville. The reverse fixture took place last month at Wembley and saw Marcus Rashford give England the lead, but first-half goals by Saul Niguez and Rodrigo Moreno gave Spain a 2-1 win. Luis Enrique's men went on to thrash Croatia 6-0 three days later, suggesting Gareth Southgate's side may face an even tougher task on Spanish soil.
